<HEADLINE> Tehran Stock Exchange Index Up Slightly </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
TEHRAN, May 16 (Xinhua) -- Tehran Stock Exchange index stood
at 1605.48 points on Saturday, up by 0.62 from Wednesday when the
last trading week ended.
</P>
<P>
The stock market closed on Thursday and Friday.
</P>
<P>
A total of 648,658 shares worth more than 3.92 billion Iranian
rials (about 871,111 U.S. dollars) were traded in the day.
