"All the Palestinian brothers, regardless of their
affiliations, factions and orientations, should foil the designs
of their enemies who seek to sow dissension and dissipation among
them," he said.
</P>
<P>
The Yemeni president spoke highly of Yassin's struggle and his
role to consolidate the unity of the sons of Palestine.
</P>
<P>
On his part. Yassin thanked the Yemeni leader and voiced
appreciation for Yemen's support for the struggle of the
Palestinian people.
</P>
<P>
During the meeting, the two leaders discussed the latest
developments in the Mideast and the stalemate of the Middle East
peace process.
</P>
<P>
Yassin, who arrived here Thursday, is on a tour of Muslim
countries. 
</P>
</TEXT>
