<HEADLINE> Venezuela Crudes Basket Price Continues to Fall </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
CARACAS, May 16 (Xinhua) -- Venezuela's crudes basket was
quoted at 11.32 dollars per barrel at the end of this week, well
below the 1997 average price of 16.32 dollars.
</P>
<P>
A weekly report by the Venezuelan Energy and Mines Ministry
shows that the crudes basket has maintained a downward line so far
this year.
</P>
<P>
